panels.title: Users

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  CASE 
    WHEN b.first_name = 'Admin' THEN b.first_name
    ELSE CONCAT(b.first_name, ' ', b.last_name)
  END AS full_name,
  a.*
FROM cosmologo_dev.admin_notify_groups_view a
LEFT JOIN users b
  ON a.owner_id = b.id
ORDER BY 
  CASE WHEN b.first_name = 'Admin' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END,  -- Admin rows first
  b.first_name, 
  a.title

SELECT 
  title
FROM 
  cosmologo_dev.admin_notify_groups_service_view
UNION ALL 
SELECT
  'None' AS title
ORDER BY 
  CASE WHEN title = 'None' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END,
  title

SELECT 'TOP LEFT' AS position UNION ALL
SELECT 'TOP MIDDLE' UNION ALL
SELECT 'TOP RIGHT' UNION ALL
SELECT 'MIDDLE LEFT' UNION ALL
SELECT 'MIDDLE MIDDLE' UNION ALL
SELECT 'MIDDLE RIGHT' UNION ALL
SELECT 'BOTTOM LEFT' UNION ALL
SELECT 'BOTTOM MIDDLE' UNION ALL
SELECT 'BOTTOM RIGHT'

SELECT 'DELETE' AS email, '' AS title
UNION
( 
  SELECT 
    a.email,
    b.title 
  FROM cosmologo_dev.users a
  LEFT JOIN cosmologo_dev.users_role_types_table b
  ON a.role_id = b.id 
  WHERE b.title != 'ADMIN' OR b.title IS NULL
  ORDER BY email
)

(
  SELECT 
    CONCAT(first_name, ' ', last_name, ' USER') COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci AS target_name
  FROM users
  WHERE role_id != (
    SELECT id 
    FROM cosmologo_dev.users_role_types_table
    WHERE title = 'ADMIN'
  )
  ORDER BY target_name
  LIMIT 18446744073709551615 -- Forces MySQL to honor the ORDER BY
)
UNION
(
  SELECT
    CONCAT(title, ' GROUP') COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci AS target_name
  FROM users_groups_table
  WHERE owner_id = (
    SELECT 
      id 
    FROM users 
    WHERE role_id = (
        SELECT id FROM users_role_types_table
        WHERE title = 'ADMIN'
    )
  )
  ORDER BY target_name
  LIMIT 18446744073709551615 -- Forces MySQL to honor the ORDER BY
);

(
  SELECT 
    CONCAT(first_name, ' ', last_name, ' USER') COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci AS target_name
  FROM users
  WHERE role_id in (
    SELECT id 
    FROM cosmologo_dev.users_role_types_table
    WHERE title in ('PATIENT','SERVICE_PROVIDER')
  )
  ORDER BY target_name
  LIMIT 18446744073709551615 -- Forces MySQL to honor the ORDER BY
)
UNION
(
  SELECT
    CONCAT(title, ' GROUP') COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci AS target_name
  FROM users_groups_table
  WHERE owner_id = (
    SELECT 
      id 
    FROM users 
    WHERE role_id = (
        SELECT id FROM users_role_types_table
        WHERE title = 'ADMIN'
    )
  )
  ORDER BY target_name
  LIMIT 18446744073709551615 -- Forces MySQL to honor the ORDER BY
);

SELECT
  (
    SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(JSON_UNQUOTE(msg.message) SEPARATOR ' | ')  -- FIXED
    FROM JSON_TABLE(
      a.messages,
      '$[*]' COLUMNS(
        ordinal FOR ORDINALITY,
        message JSON PATH '$'
      )
    ) AS msg
  ) AS promo,
  a.id
FROM notify_promotions_table a
ORDER BY promo

SELECT 
  id,
  title 
FROM 
cosmologo_dev.users_groups_table 
WHERE owner_id = (
  SELECT id
  FROM cosmologo_dev.users
  WHERE role_id = (
    SELECT id
    FROM cosmologo_dev.users_role_types_table
    WHERE title = 'ADMIN'
  )
)

SELECT 
  id,title 
FROM cosmologo_dev.appointments_assignments_status_types_table
WHERE title IN ('PENDING','ACCEPTED')

SELECT 
  title 
FROM 
  cosmologo_dev.appointments_history_change_status_types_table 
WHERE title NOT IN ('CANCELLED','DISCARDED')

SELECT DISTINCT
  a.id,
  CONCAT(a.first_name,' ',a.last_name) AS full_name
FROM users a
INNER JOIN users_role_types_table r 
  ON a.role_id = r.id 
  AND r.title = 'SERVICE_PROVIDER'
ORDER BY full_name

SELECT DISTINCT
  a.id,
  CONCAT(a.first_name,' ',a.last_name) AS full_name
FROM users a
INNER JOIN users_role_types_table r 
  ON a.role_id = r.id 
  AND r.title = 'PATIENT'
ORDER BY full_name

SELECT 
  a.id,
  CONCAT(c.title,' - ', d.title) AS title
FROM cosmologo_dev.services_products_table a
LEFT JOIN cosmologo_dev.services_treatments_table c
ON a.service_treatment_id = c.id
LEFT JOIN cosmologo_dev.services_body_parts_table d
ON a.service_body_part_id = d.id
ORDER BY title

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
	c.title AS treatment,
	CONCAT(a.first_name,' ',a.last_name) AS full_name
FROM users a
LEFT JOIN services_table b
ON a.id = b.service_provider_id
LEFT JOIN services_products_table d
ON b.service_product_id = d.id
LEFT JOIN services_treatments_table c
ON d.service_treatment_id = c.id
WHERE role_id = (SELECT id FROM users_role_types_table WHERE title = 'SERVICE_PROVIDER') 
ORDER BY full_name,treatment

SELECT DISTINCT
  a.id,
  CONCAT(a.first_name,' ',a.last_name) AS full_name
FROM users a
INNER JOIN users_role_types_table r 
  ON a.role_id = r.id 
  AND r.title = 'SERVICE_PROVIDER'
ORDER BY full_name
